  "text": "RT-QuIC data were analyzed as previously described [CITATION_1] . Briefly, to compensate for differences between the plate readers, we averaged data from replicate wells and normalized to a percentage of the maximal fluorescence response of the instrument. The obtained values were plotted against the reaction times.",
